33:59.400 --> 34:00.480
Awak Xia Dajun?

34:03.240 --> 34:04.500
Dia panggil nama awak.

34:05.690 --> 34:07.820
Kenapa kamu datang ke Kampung Qijing?

34:08.760 --> 34:09.630
Bagaimana... bagaimana awak cakap

34:09.630 --> 34:10.630
