34:45.639 --> 34:46.400
Bukan, dia...

34:46.400 --> 34:47.330
Bukan, Xiaolan.

34:47.440 --> 34:48.510
Kenapa awak cakap begini?

34:48.510 --> 34:49.030
Awak ialah orang muda,

34:49.030 --> 34:50.000
